<div class="page-header">
  <div class="media">
    <div class="pull-left">
      <%= image_tag 'clients.png', class: 'media-object' %>
    </div>
    <div class="media-body">
      <h1>Import Clients</h1>
      <%= link_to clients_path do
      %><%= fa_icon 'arrow-left', text: 'Back' %>

      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<%= form_tag clients_imports_path, multipart: true do |f| %>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span5">
        <%= file_field_tag :file, style: 'display:none;', id: 'upload-clients' %>
        <div class="input-append">
          <%= text_field_tag nil, nil, class: 'input-large', id: 'upload-clients-file' %>
          <a class="btn" onclick="$('input[id=upload-clients]').click();">Browse</a>
        </div>
        <br>
        <%= submit_tag 'Import Clients', class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
      </div>
      <div class="span6 well">
        <div class="media">
          <div class="pull-left">
            <%= image_tag 'tip.png', class: 'media-object' %>
          </div>
          <div class="media-body">
            <h3 class="media-heading">Notes:</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="form-notes">
          <li><strong>File:</strong> Use the browse button to select the spreadsheet you wish to import.</li>
          <li>
            <strong>Format:</strong> The first row of the spreadsheet needs to contain the following headers:
            <ul>
              <li><strong>BusinessName:</strong> The business name of the client. (This field is not optional)</li>
              <li><strong>Email:</strong> The email of the client. (This field is not optional)</li>
              <li><strong>ContactPerson:</strong> The email of the client. (This field is optional)</li>
              <li><strong>Address:</strong> The address of the client. (This field is optional)</li>
              <li><strong>City:</strong> The city of the client. (This field is optional)</li>
              <li><strong>PostCode:</strong> The post code of the client. (This field is optional)</li>
              <li><strong>Telephone:</strong> The telephone number of the client. (This field is optional)</li>
              <li><strong>Fax:</strong> The fax number of the client. (This field is optional)</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>When the records are imported, the system will check whether the business name exists and if so update the
            existing client.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
<% end %>
